Dzimwe nguva, undiona ndakanyarara kwazvo.

0:22:09.280,0:22:17.480
Zvose zvamaive muchitaura pamusoro pezvangu kwemakore makumi matatu adarika, "Ndiri ichi kana icho" - Handitaure.

0:22:17.480,0:22:19.160
Ichi ndicho chikonzero.

0:22:19.160,0:22:21.960
Ndange ndakangwarira zvikuru.

0:22:21.960,0:22:31.740
Iwe unogona kundituka, kutaura zvinhu zvese zvese pamusoro pezvangu; Handitauri - Ini ndinozvitora pachangu ku munamato

0:22:31.740,0:22:39.660
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:22:39.660,0:22:55.280
Mumwe munhu ari dhiyabhorosi kwauri,  marwadzo kwauri nhasi anogona kuve muponesi mangwana.

0:22:55.280,0:22:59.080
Iwe unogona kuva chero zvauri kwandiri nhasi.

0:22:59.080,0:23:14.100
Kana iwe ukachinja kuva dhiyabhorosi nhasi, ini ndichatarira mberi kwako kuti ndione kuti iwe ungave chii mangwana.

0:23:14.100,0:23:19.140
Mangwana akavanzika.

0:23:19.140,0:23:23.740
Ukama - chenjerera.

0:23:23.740,0:23:33.680
Munhu uyo ari muvengi wako nhasi anogona kuva muponesi wako mangwana.

0:23:33.680,0:23:44.360
Kana ukaramba uchishandisa zviito zvevanhu nhasi kuti uvatonge, unogona kuva nezvinetso munguva inotevera.

0:23:44.360,0:23:51.460
"Murume wacho akaipa kwazvo." Mukadzi wacho akaipa kwazvo. " - nokuti vakaipa kwazvo iwe unoita chimwe chinhu;

0:23:51.460,0:23:55.860
iwe uchave ne matambudziko mangwana.

0:23:55.860,0:24:05.260
Iwe uchagamuchira munguva pfupi icho wange uchitsvaga kwemakore apo iwe unorega chigumbuso chichienda.

0:24:05.260,0:24:11.980
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:24:11.980,0:24:18.940
Ungave wagona kana kutadza, uchichengeta chigumbu kune muvakidzani wako -

0:24:18.940,0:24:21.800
iwe wato shungurudza Mweya Mutsvene -

0:24:21.800,0:24:37.220
nokuti uri mweya, unorarama mumuviri wenyama, uchidzidza kurarama munyika sezvairi.

0:24:37.220,0:24:54.100
Taura kwauri pachako, "Ini ndiri mweya, ndino rarama mumuviri wenyama, ndichidzidza kurarama munyika sezvairi".

0:24:54.100,0:25:02.040
Kana iwe uri mweya, sei iwe uri kurwisana nehama yako?

0:25:02.040,0:25:06.480
Hondo yedu haisi ye kurwisa nyama ne ropa.

0:25:06.480,0:25:12.100
Hama yako ndeye ropa ne nyama.

0:25:12.100,0:25:17.760
Iwe uri mweya uye hondo yako haisi kurwisa nyama ne ropa asi kurwisana ne vanhu ve mweya.

0:25:17.760,0:25:21.240
Kushushikana ne kuomerwa.

0:25:21.240,0:25:26.480
Bvunza waugere naye, "Sei uri kurwisa hama dzako?"

0:25:26.480,0:25:33.540
Ivo inyama ne ropa uye hondo yako haisi yekurwisana nenyama neropa.

0:25:33.540,0:25:46.200
Iwe uri mweya, unorarama mumuviri wenyama, uchidzidza kurarama munyika sezvairi.

0:25:46.200,0:25:53.080
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:25:53.080,0:25:59.620
Iwe unofanirwa kurega nyika izive kuti uri mweya nekuita nenzira iyi,

0:25:59.620,0:26:02.860
nokusarwisana nenyama neropa.

0:26:02.860,0:26:13.480
Kana hama yako ichiti, "Ndichaona zvekuita newe", iwe unoti pachako, "Ndiri mweya, iwe unogona sei kuona chekuita nemweya?"

0:26:13.480,0:26:19.140
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:26:19.140,0:26:21.120
Unoona zvekuita ne mweya sei? Hazvibviri.

0:26:21.120,0:26:24.280
Iwe haugone kubata kana kugunzva mweya.

0:26:24.280,0:26:27.720
Uchaona kupi ne kurwisa mweya?

0:26:27.720,0:26:31.960
Iwe unogona kurwisana nenyama neropa chete.

0:26:31.960,0:26:42.580
Jesu akataura zvakanyatsojeka kuti hazvigoneki kurarama munyika ino pasina kukanganisirwa.

0:26:42.580,0:26:49.040
Chigumbuso chichauya - usachichengete.

0:26:49.040,0:26:54.940
Chigumboso pachezvacho hachina kunyanya kuipa.

0:26:54.940,0:26:58.160
Chichauya; usachichengeta.

0:26:58.160,0:27:03.900
Ndeapo paunenge uchichengeta chigumbu mumwoyo mako apo chinobereka

0:27:03.900,0:27:16.620
hasha, ruvengo, kutsoropodza, kutsamwa uye kukakavara.

0:27:16.620,0:27:24.120
Kana kukabereka marwadzo ne hasha, iwe hauchafara zvakare.

0:27:24.120,0:27:31.800
"Hareruya" rudairo runobva pamwoyo unofara.

0:27:31.800,0:27:41.760
Kusafara kunogona kukanganisa ukama hwako na Mwari, nevamwe uye hutano hwako.

0:27:41.760,0:27:44.460
Fara.

0:27:44.460,0:28:02.940
Kuti iwe ufare, unofanira kuvimba nesimba ra Mwari kupfuura ruzhinji rwevanhu.

0:28:02.940,0:28:06.860
Ndinoda kutenda kuti wasununguka zvino.

0:28:06.860,0:28:08.020
(Ameni!)

0:28:08.020,0:28:11.400
Wasununguka here? - (Ehe!)

0:28:11.400,0:28:15.840
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:28:15.840,0:28:22.080
Rudaviro urwu runobva pamwoyo unofara.

0:28:22.080,0:28:26.000
- Wasununguka here? - (Ehe!)

0:28:26.000,0:28:33.160
(Ndasununguka!)

0:28:33.160,0:28:35.700
Iwe unorevei nekuti "iwe wasununguka"?

0:28:35.700,0:28:39.120
Ndasununguka mumwoyo mangu.

0:28:39.120,0:28:42.540
Nomweya mumwoyo mangu.

0:28:42.540,0:28:44.180
Nomweya? - Ehe.

0:28:44.180,0:28:50.320
Ndinoda kukutenda kuti iwe unoteerera kuzwi remweya wako nokuti rinotungamirirwa ne Mweya Mutsvene.

0:28:50.320,0:28:55.500
Iwe unofanirwa kufidha mweya wako; mweya wako une nzara.

0:28:55.500,0:29:00.260
Iwe unogara uchipa chekudya kunyama yako asi iwe uri mweya.

0:29:00.260,0:29:03.660
Nzara inoda kuuraya mweya wako.

0:29:03.660,0:29:10.000
Zvokudya izvi zvose zvaunodya hazvisi zvemweya wako, ndezvenyama yako.

0:29:10.000,0:29:15.500
Unofanira kupa chekudya ku mweya wako nekubvumira Shoko ra Mwari.

0:29:15.500,0:29:21.240
Verenga Shoko ra Mwari, fungisisa nezvaro uye richengete mumwoyo mako.

0:29:21.240,0:29:28.060
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:29:28.060,0:29:36.520
Shoko reuporofita iro Mwari akandipa nderokuti Iye aizobata mwoyo wako nemharidzo iyi.

0:29:36.520,0:29:39.880
Ndiri kuona kuti mwoyo wako wabatwa.

0:29:39.880,0:29:42.420
(Ameni.)

0:29:42.420,0:29:48.320
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:29:48.320,0:29:52.820
Kune vanhu vakawanda vausingadi kunzwa kubva kwavari.

0:29:52.820,0:29:59.880
Vafonere; ungoti, "Hi, ndinonamata newe, ndinokuda."

0:29:59.880,0:30:01.740
Izvi zvichaenda nenzira.

0:30:01.740,0:30:14.080
Mweya waka simba ne nyasha dzo uyo akadzikama mu Shoko ra Mwari unogona kuziva zvakanaka kubva mune zvakaipa,

0:30:14.080,0:30:24.020
kuparadzanisa zvakanaka kubva kune zvakaipa ne kuziva miteyo yake sezvairi.

0:30:24.020,0:30:28.280
Iwe haugoni kungoti, "Ndasununguka".

0:30:28.280,0:30:37.460
Izvozvi, tanga kuyananisa uye urege kuisa pfungwa pane zvakaipa zvavakakuitira.

0:30:37.460,0:30:43.960
Satani anoda kuti iwe uise pfungwa pane zvakaipa zvawakaitirwa ne vanhu.

0:30:43.960,0:30:45.720
Vanhu vanofanira kukuudza ...

0:30:45.720,0:30:53.540
Kune vazhinji vedu pano vanochengeta umwe, vaviri kana vanhu vatatu mujeri nekuda kwako.

0:30:53.540,0:30:55.480
Iwe wakavatongera kutirongo.

0:30:55.480,0:31:01.920
Tsvaga nguva yekuenda kujeri unoti unoda kuona munhu nhingi nhingi.

0:31:01.920,0:31:07.940
Panguva yaunopinda iwe unoti, "Munondiziva, ndapota, ndinoda kunyengetera nemi."

0:31:07.940,0:31:13.640
Tanga kufunga nezvekuti ungasunungura sei munhu akadaro kubva mujeri.

0:31:13.640,0:31:18.880
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:31:18.880,0:31:20.880
Iwe uneni here?

0:31:20.880,0:31:22.200
Paunobva pano ...

0:31:22.200,0:31:32.880
Kune vanhu vazhinji vari mujeri nokuti vakakutadzira zve chokwadi, vakakuitira zvakaipa.

0:31:32.880,0:31:38.080
Tsvaga kwavari kuchengeterwa uvashanyire.

0:31:38.080,0:31:46.320
Pinda mujeri, mirira munhu wacho, raira munhu wacho, nyengetera nemunhu wacho, uye uudze munhu wacho

0:31:46.320,0:31:50.920
kuti kubva panguva ino unoda munhu uyu kuti abuditswe kunze, kuitira kuti vagone kusunungura munhu uyu.

0:31:50.920,0:31:53.540
Regedza mhosva yacho.

0:31:53.540,0:31:58.900
Zvinhu izvozvo hazvina kunaka kune remangwana rako.

0:31:58.900,0:32:06.340
Ishe anoti, "Ndichagadzira tafura pamberi pe vanhu wavakaisa mujeri."

0:32:06.340,0:32:10.740
Kana ukavaisa mutirongo kana kuvauraya, ukavaparadza ...

0:32:10.740,0:32:15.940
Panguva iyo Mwari anogadzira tafura vanenge vasisipo asi Akavimbisa kuti Achakugadzirira tafura

0:32:15.940,0:32:22.540
pamberi pevanhu vawakaisa mutirongo.

0:32:22.540,0:32:28.800
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:32:28.800,0:32:36.900
Udza waugere naye, "Ndichagadzira tafura pamberi pako pahuso hwaani?"

0:32:36.900,0:32:48.260
Uyu muvengi - wauri kuuraya, kuparadza, kuendesa kujeri nekuda  kwe simba nechinzvimbo chaunacho

0:32:48.260,0:32:58.860
uye kodzero, mutemo we rudzi rwako, nyika yako, vazhinji vakatongerwa kufa, kujeri, kuurayiwa ...

0:32:58.860,0:33:06.880
Saka, panguva iyo Mwari achagadzira tafura iyoyo pamberi pako, pahuso hwaani?

0:33:06.880,0:33:10.640
... vanhu vawakauraya.

0:33:10.640,0:33:13.320
Vanhu vawakaparadza.

0:33:13.320,0:33:18.540
Ndokusaka tafura iyi iri kunonoka kune vazhinji vedu pano.

0:33:18.540,0:33:21.800
Pari zvino, vazhinji vedu tingadai tirikufadzwa ne tafura iyi,

0:33:21.800,0:33:25.760
asi apo Ishe vakaziva kuti iwe wakauraya, wakaparadza vavengi vako vazhinji

0:33:25.780,0:33:31.080
kana kuti wakavatumira kujeri - tafura haisisina basa.

0:33:31.080,0:33:32.620
Funga nezvazvo.

0:33:32.620,0:33:41.600
Shandura rudzi rwemunyengetero waunopa, "ifa ifa ifa" - usavauraya, regai vararame

0:33:41.600,0:33:46.540
kuti vaone tafura iyo Ishe achagadzira pamberi pako.

0:33:46.540,0:33:55.680
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:33:55.680,0:34:02.700
Edza nepaunogona kutanga kusunungura avo vaunoti muvengi chero kupi zvako kwavari;

0:34:02.700,0:34:10.520
mujeri, pose, chero kupi - sangana navo, varaire, vasiye.

0:34:10.520,0:34:15.480
Ndapota, zvakakosha zvikuru kune ramangwana rako.

0:34:15.480,0:34:21.340
Nokuda kweramangwana, kukanganwirwa kunokosha zvikuru.

0:34:21.340,0:34:25.940
Nekuda kweramangwana rako, kusunungurwa kwevavengi vako kunokosha zvikuru.

0:34:25.940,0:34:27.840
Mwari vakukomborerei.

